  m_Name: Email_Day03_03
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::EmailData
  senderName: Content Corp. Operations
  senderAddress: ops@content-corp.net
  subject: 'New tool: Replace function now available'
  body: 'Dear Moderator,


    We have added a new moderation action: REPLACE.


    When
    you encounter posts containing distressing or alarmist content, you may now replace
    them with pre-approved positive content from our library.


    Example: A post
    about a ''city lockdown'' can be replaced with a post about a ''community festival''.


    This
    reduces viewer anxiety and maintains platform trust.


    Thank you for your
    continued dedication.


    Operations Team

    Content Corp.'
  showOnDay: 3
